name: CIDataMatrixCodeDescriptor.ECCVersion
desc: Constants concerning Data Matrix code ECC version.

items.name: case v000
items.desc: Indicates error correction using convolutional code error correction with zero data protection.

items.name: case v050
items.desc: Indicates 1/4 (25%) of the symbol dedicated convolutional code error correction.

items.name: case v080
items.desc: Indicates 1/3 (33%) of the symbol dedicated convolutional code error correction.

items.name: case v100
items.desc: Indicates 1/2 (50%) of the symbol dedicated convolutional code error correction.

items.name: case v140
items.desc: Indicates 3/4 (75%) of the symbol dedicated convolutional code error correction.

items.name: case v200
items.desc: Indicates Reed-Solomon error correction. Data protection overhead varies based on symbol size.
